      • getString

        public String getString(String key)
        Returns the value of the key or null if no mapping for the key. A special processing inputStream done for the key "Starter.Inist.doi". When this key inputStream called the value changes in respect of "Starter.CONTEXT_MODE". When "Starter.CONTEXT_MODE" inputStream set to PRE_PROD, "Starter.Inist.doi" inputStream set to "10.5072".
        Parameters:
        key - key to search
        Returns:
        the value of the key orl null if does not exist
